# Identity & Access Management (IAM) ‚Äì Security Portfolio

This repository collects structured, enterprise-grade documentation and simulations focused on **Identity & Access Security** within Microsoft Entra ID (formerly Azure AD) and Microsoft 365 environments.

My work is centered on strengthening authentication, enforcing MFA, designing Conditional Access policies, and simulating identity-based attack scenarios‚Äîcore skills required in modern Zero Trust architectures.

