## üìÑ Included Projects

### ‚úî MFA Inventory ‚Äì EVM Rail
A real-world MFA adoption assessment conducted across 11 users.  
Includes:
- user risk classification  
- authentication method review  
- exposure analysis  
- operational plan for MFA rollout  

Demonstrates familiarity with Microsoft 365 authentication flows and identity risks.

---

### ‚úî Conditional Access ‚Äì Baseline Policy Design
A complete baseline Conditional Access blueprint, covering:
- Block Legacy Authentication  
- MFA for all users  
- MFA for administrative roles  
- High-risk sign-in protection  
- Geo-blocking guidelines  
- Zero Trust device considerations  

Shows ability to design enforceable identity security controls.

---

### ‚úî Incident Simulation ‚Äì Password Spray Attack
A realistic simulation highlighting:
- detection using Entra ID logs  
- early indicators  
- IAM-focused response steps  
- mitigation via Conditional Access & MFA  
- attacker behavior patterns  

Demonstrates analytical thinking and security reasoning.

---

### ‚úî Incident Simulation ‚Äì MFA Fatigue (Push Bombing)
Documents one of the most common modern MFA-bypass attempts.  
Covers:
- attack pattern  
- log indicators  
- user behavior exploitation  
- remediation  
- hardening with number matching and stronger factors  

Shows understanding of identity attack vectors and modern defenses.

